Settings->Grid Settings

This selection brings up the Grid Settings editor. This editor has
more options on the grid that is displayed in the main Movieola
window. Parameters like grid divisions, subdivisions, axis size and
snap divisions/subdivisions may be set in this editor. You can also
turn on/off the "Snap to Grid" option in Movieola. When this option is
on, Movieola objects snap to line sub-divisions in the grid when they
are moved
